# No New Tests

Do not create new permanent test files or test cases in the `tests/` directory.

- Do not add files under `tests/` (e.g. `test_*.py`, `*_test.py`).
- Do not expand existing test files with new test functions or classes unless the user explicitly asks.
- If a change would benefit from tests, mention that to the user instead of writing them.

Existing tests may be updated only when the user explicitly requests test changes.
